{"tid":29802,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人應該死咗去算","createTime":"2016-12-08T20:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T11:22:50.000Z","uid":35911,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"763e81e9f66914b1a3a46ab90900f901af8528f6","tid":29802,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T20:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇權冇勢,畀人恰都冇得反抗,諗緊向邊到死好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw冇錢唔好生仔,除非你唔怕個仔憎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd60426a9069f319a5a056d0246e4777f49ba63","tid":29802,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T20:08:17.000Z","msg":"巴打畀啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4db1e90fd48b0bbba56e4ce87791c108578843","tid":29802,"uid":14797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T20:13:22.000Z","msg":"未裸跑喎"},{"pid":"b7db23117559ec280f07f225af37048d3a7b2755","tid":29802,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T20:14:35.000Z","msg":"見裸跑post過半，個勢唔多對路想搵定後路呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b45b7e4a385d60f55ff53a50cc5fd5a08cbfcf5","tid":29802,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T20:17:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"407164106951ba172fea4cb440c4ff7d53651242","tid":29802,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T20:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見裸跑post過半，個勢唔多對路想搵定後路呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未過五千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca73c152e6c21d86d13c27022ca5bd75c17f081","tid":29802,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T20:35:26.000Z","msg":"召喚gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b955637dbbc6d19d35dbbe116c671ff11f18a9","tid":29802,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T20:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真有死嘅意願<br />\n<br />\n但想報答父母<br />\n<br />\n點樣可以死前賺五十萬或以上畀家人?<br />\n<br />\n唔好講借財仔 - 有住址證明, 佢哋會搵得到我家人嘔返錢出來<br />\n<br />\n唔好講碌爆卡套現 - 合共得幾皮, 遠遠唔夠啦<br />\n<br />\n供份保單然後死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又等唔切, 已經好想死了, 唔想再慢慢供<br />\n<br />\n有冇計? 請鬼仔? 筆仙碟仙? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 折壽又好咩都好 有錢就得 反正求死</blockquote><br />\n買六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw自殺應該保單唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792ce8fac6472069d3e04dd813451f3787cc5cb4","tid":29802,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T20:42:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dafedc43070c5fa9008bc812db21c159bf8a30fd","tid":29802,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T21:11:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"505b4b328d8c2672685e0738d3ee7d8db8f373af","tid":29802,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T21:12:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4344ec9aa7c29cfb2b55cef892374b3ab9e4cd78","tid":29802,"uid":54777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T21:16:56.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔，正仆街.gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59f1e49f9a97aa58a533b763f90b5e3b8244590","tid":29802,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-0